		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Shepherd druids are especially attuned to the grasslands, plains, and savannahs of the world. They act as guides and for creatures of the wild and their adventuring allies.</em></p><p><em>This subclass is a reimagining of a classic archetype and is not based on preexisting subclasses with the same name.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Shepherd</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.rEgvy8ZFH9bI19ym]{Herd's Swiftness}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.rZnOiGzvXijlzUEU]{Stampede}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.zP5V7P953Sx6CjAt]{Shepherd's Ward}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.5jipgSZPDIWFHoet]{Calm the Herd}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.rX9Y6L97pIXb64K1]{Aspect of the Plains}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Druid Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Extra Spells</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.NpFvVJ2qYoRpDAw8]{Bless}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.I80JFUFkSDeMFgXF]{Cure Wounds}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.qmpljuHtwKkER2xa]{Enthrall}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.9euw3Uj4JcV3GnaP]{Pass without Trace}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.lul0V4xIEqxIhJaZ]{Haste}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.wdMMuMxLQPrfvcXv]{Phantom Steed}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>7</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.7iQOTB9TMvb3MfSn]{Faithful Hound}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Y24nyCt4lQreT5aH]{Freedom of Movement}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>9</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.VkpZOMVqwichvUXA]{Mass Cure Wounds}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.kj85kLkGaxNuoGKz]{Telepathic Bond}</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
